Logical_source_description.0: AMS-02 proton flux (p), helium flux (He), p/He flux ratio, electron flux (e-), positron flux (e+) and e+/e- flux ratio at Bartels rotation time resolution

VarAttributes.CATDESC: Default time
Bartels rotation number.
Left edge of proton bin.
Right edge of proton bin.
Proton differential flux, at 45 bins 0.433-59.37 GeV/n.
Proton flux total error: statistical and systematic added in quadrature.
Proton flux statistical error.
Proton fluxtime-dependent error: trigger and reconstruction efficiency errors added in quadrature.

Proton Flux systematic error: acceptance, background contamination, geomagnetic cutoff, event selection, rigidity resolution, unfolding, absolute rigidity scale and time-dependent errors added in quadrature.

p/He ratio systematic error: p and He systematic errors added in quadrature, with correlations in rigidity resolution, unfolding, absolute rigidity scale errors taken into account.
